            <title>realme 真我 Neo7 手机首个跑分曝光：天玑 9300+ 处理器，7000mAh 电池</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/812/996.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/812/996.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:14:58 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1310370" rel="nofollow">偏科骚黄4100只眼</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2136589" rel="nofollow">零刑</a> 的线索投递！</div>
